                <note rend="inline" type="source">717.2114/70: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Minister in Colombia</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Piles</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1928-09-15T13:00:00-04:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">September 15, 1928—1 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>55. Has text of treaty between Colombia and Nicaragua of March 24 last been made
                    public in Colombia?</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Kellogg</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
